    "advancement": [],
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong data-start=\"343\" data-end=\"386\">Echoes of Glory (Special; 1/Short Rest)</strong><br data-start=\"386\" data-end=\"389\" />Your deeds linger in the air, inspiring allies and unnerving foes.</p><p data-start=\"457\" data-end=\"625\">When you <strong data-start=\"466\" data-end=\"503\">reduce a creature to 0 hit points</strong>, you may choose <strong data-start=\"520\" data-end=\"551\">one creature within 30 feet</strong> that can see or hear you. Until the <strong data-start=\"588\" data-end=\"624\">end of that creature’s next turn</strong>:</p><ul data-start=\"627\" data-end=\"803\"><li data-start=\"627\" data-end=\"709\"><p data-start=\"629\" data-end=\"709\">If the creature is an <strong data-start=\"651\" data-end=\"659\">ally</strong>, it gains <strong data-start=\"670\" data-end=\"708\">advantage on its next saving throw</strong>.</p></li><li data-start=\"710\" data-end=\"803\"><p data-start=\"712\" data-end=\"803\">If the creature is a <strong data-start=\"733\" data-end=\"753\">hostile creature</strong>, it has <strong data-start=\"762\" data-end=\"802\">disadvantage on its next attack roll</strong>.</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"805\" data-end=\"898\">Once you use this feature, you cannot use it again until you finish a <strong data-start=\"875\" data-end=\"897\">short or long rest</strong>.</p><hr data-start=\"900\" data-end=\"903\" /><p data-start=\"905\" data-end=\"962\">Optional script tag:<br /><code data-start=\"926\" data-end=\"962\">[GAROU_FEATURE] id=echoes-of-glory</code></p>",
      "chat": "<p><strong data-start=\"343\" data-end=\"386\">Echoes of Glory (Special; 1/Short Rest)</strong><br data-start=\"386\" data-end=\"389\" />Your deeds linger in the air, inspiring allies and unnerving foes.</p><p data-start=\"457\" data-end=\"625\">When you <strong data-start=\"466\" data-end=\"503\">reduce a creature to 0 hit points</strong>, you may choose <strong data-start=\"520\" data-end=\"551\">one creature within 30 feet</strong> that can see or hear you. Until the <strong data-start=\"588\" data-end=\"624\">end of that creature’s next turn</strong>:</p><ul data-start=\"627\" data-end=\"803\"><li data-start=\"627\" data-end=\"709\"><p data-start=\"629\" data-end=\"709\">If the creature is an <strong data-start=\"651\" data-end=\"659\">ally</strong>, it gains <strong data-start=\"670\" data-end=\"708\">advantage on its next saving throw</strong>.</p></li><li data-start=\"710\" data-end=\"803\"><p data-start=\"712\" data-end=\"803\">If the creature is a <strong data-start=\"733\" data-end=\"753\">hostile creature</strong>, it has <strong data-start=\"762\" data-end=\"802\">disadvantage on its next attack roll</strong>.</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"805\" data-end=\"898\">Once you use this feature, you cannot use it again until you finish a <strong data-start=\"875\" data-end=\"897\">short or long rest</strong>.</p><hr data-start=\"900\" data-end=\"903\" /><p data-start=\"905\" data-end=\"962\"></p>"
